text: Oberschrot was a municipality in the district of Sense in the canton of Fribourg in Switzerland. On 1 January 2017, the municipalities of Oberschrot and Zumholz became part of Plaffeien.Amtliches Gemeindeverzeichnis der Schweiz accessed 10 January 2017 == References == == Other websites == * Official website Category:Former municipalities of Fribourg
